      "cooked": "<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2021/06/16/mandibles-komedi-franceze-me-regji-te-quentin-dupieux/\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/d/b/db1cbce51481f7ac4d6d620139075d8871e7af34.jpeg\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2021/06/16/mandibles-komedi-franceze-me-regji-te-quentin-dupieux/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"10:18AM - 16 June 2021\">kinoditar – 16 Jun 21</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:247/330;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/a/8/a829bd18f8b14bc0ccba423fa510a90d6f725152.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"247\" height=\"330\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2021/06/16/mandibles-komedi-franceze-me-regji-te-quentin-dupieux/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Budallenj të të gjitha vendeve, bashkohuni ! (“Mandibles” – komedi franceze...</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Visit the post for more.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
